<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>FIR Registered</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>FIR Registration Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your FIR has been successfully registered.</p>
    <p><strong>FIR Number:</strong> {{firNumber}}</p>
    <p><strong>Complaint:</strong> {{complaint}}</p>
    <p><strong>Crime Type:</strong> {{crimeType}}</p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
    <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
    <p>You will be notified of any updates.</p>
</body>
</html>